#
# Layer discipline:
#   [kernel]     — Non-derivable physical axioms (root of derivation graph)
#   [rule]       — Structural meta-rules constraining assertion form
#   [contingent] — Universe-specific empirical facts (not kernel)
#   [law]        — Effective laws derived from kernel + contingent
#   [corollary]  — Derived from law(s)
#
# Source graph rules (V1–V5): see SOURCE.md
# Language spec (token/node/grammar): see LANGUAGE.md
# Extraction order: see EXTRACTION.md
