# R1–R6 mapping:
#   R1 → kernel.lorentz_invariance,
#         kernel.spacetime_dimensionality, kernel.equivalence_principle,
#         kernel.general_covariance
#   R2 → kernel.least_action
#   R3 → kernel.gauge_interactions
#   R4 → kernel.superposition_principle, kernel.unitary_evolution,
#         kernel.canonical_commutation, kernel.operator_observable
#         (four logically INDEPENDENT postulates — see R4.8 in rules.md)
#   R5 → kernel.born_rule
#   R6 → kernel.boltzmann_entropy, kernel.equal_prior_probability
#
# Version: Round 11 (2026-05-16) — R1-R6 necessity/sufficiency audit fixes

